            <div class="col-span-3">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h4 class="text-lg mb-6">Sidlime v lokalite:</h4>
                    <div class="w-1/2 mb-6">
                        <h2 class="text-5xl">Financny dom Kosice </h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-2/3">
                        <p>Ak preferujete osobny kontakt, pre Vas vsetkych je tu nasa centralav Kosiciach</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="centrala-top-bg1"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-4">
                <div id="centrala-top-bg2" class="flex items-center">
                    <div>
                        <img src="/images/media-placeholder.svg" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="centrala-description">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-6 flex items-center">
        <div class="col-span-2">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2">
                <div id="centrala-descrpition-bg1" class="border border-black"></div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-5xl mb-6">Centrala</h3>
                    <p class="w-11/12">
                        Nadštandardná forma starostlivosti. Náš tím expertov je vám k dispozícii v pracovné dni od 8:00
                        do 17:00. Poskytneme Vám kompletný servis od žiadosti o pôžičku až po jej schválenie. Čo je pre
                        nás dôležité? Spokojný zákazníci!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-4 border border-black">
            <div id="centrala-description-bg2">
                <div class="bg-dRed no-space">
                    <img src="/images/testt.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="centrala-location">
    <div class="flex justify-end py-32">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-7 bg-white p-16 gap-12 mr-60 rounded-lg">
            <div class="col-span-5">
                <h3 class="text-6xl">Navstivte nas</h3>
                <h4 class="text-4xl">Pre viac informacii</h4>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Consequatur, sed?</p>
            </div>
            <div id="map-card-bg" class="border border-black col-span-2"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="centrala-personal" class="flex text-secondary">
    <div id="left-personal"></div>
    <div id="personal-content">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 px-24 gap-12">
            <div class="col-span-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
                <h2 class="text-5xl mb-3">Personal</h2>
                <p class="text-sm">
                    Máme dlhoročné skúsenosti v oblasti poskytovania úverov, našou víziou je
                    prinášať klientom jednoduchú cestu k peniazom. Chápeme potrebám klientov
                    a preto im dávame na výber rýchlu možnosť požiadania o pôžičku online
                    alebo osobne u nás v centrále.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-2">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2">
                    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
                        <img src="/images/person1.png" alt="">
                        <div class="w-1/2 mt-9">
                            <span class="text-center text-xl">Adrian Kudlac</span>
                            <span class="text-center text-sm text-dRed">Riaditel centraly</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col justify-end items-center">
                        <img src="/images/person2.png" alt="">
                        <div class="w-1/2 mt-9">
                            <span class="text-center text-xl">Adrian Kudlac</span>
                            <span class="text-center text-sm text-dRed">Riaditel centraly</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="right-personal"></div>
</section>
<section id="centrala-contact">
    <div id="centrala-contact-content" class="grid grid-cols-5 bg-white mx-auto p-24 rounded-lg drop-shadow-xl">
        <div class="col-span-2">
            <h2 class="text-6xl mb-4">Kontaktujte nas</h2>
            <p>V pracovné dni od 8:00 do 17:00</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-2 mx-auto">
            <div class="flex items-center mt-10">
                <img src="/images/contact-call.svg" alt="" class="w-8">
                <span class="ml-7 text-xl">+421 918 709 028</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center mt-5">
                <img src="/images/contact-mail.svg" alt="" class="w-8">
                <span class="ml-7 text-xl">info@bestpozicky.sk</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center mt-5">
                <img src="/images/contact-location.svg" alt="" class="w-8">
                <span class="ml-7 text-xl">Fejova 1, 040 01 Kosice</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-1" id="contact-right"></div>
    </div>
</section>